evidently uppermost in her mind.
It was blasphemy to God, and an outrage to
man. Let him look to it, I say, for his soul is in
cruel jeopardy!
A heavy sigh was the answer of the
Burgomaster's
wife.
I knew young Odo von Ritterstein well,
continued
